HEADWORD: Thalamiflorous
<hw>Thal`a*mi*flo"rous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[See <er>Thalamus</er>, and <er>Floral</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Bearing the stamens directly on the receptacle;
-- said of a subclass of polypetalous dicotyledonous plants in the
system of De Candolle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

